IN RE Resignation of SKELTON 2018-0924 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 4, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

Sua sponte, James Ralph Skelton, Attorney Registration No. 0067828, last known business address in Independence, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to surrender his attorney-registration card, failure to surrender his certificate of admission, and failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before August 27, 2018.
